EYEYE👁️

Just a little something to share, a minute isn’t enough capture the magic of this show and the talent and kindness of everyone apart. 

I never imagined I would get to share the stage with you @lykkeli but all I can say is thank you for having me on this journey with you. I have forever admired the artist and woman you are and to share this space with you was beyond what I could have asked for. You are incredible and I will forever love twirling with you.

A very huge heartfelt thank you to everyone on this team for having me, you are some of the most beautiful, talented and incredible artists I have met. From beginning rehearsals, to starting tour, to exploring cities, dinner nights, to laughs on and off the stage, it was an honor to share this space and time with you. 

Until we see each other again, I love you and thank you.❤️

Haven’t gotten to share this yet but this was the last show of tour & the energy in this room was unreal. Pure exploration of the chemical reactions of love. Cheers to more love ahead. 

Love sharing this space with you @lykkeli ❣️
